來會有怎樣的演變仍然難說。值得一提的是，模擬中世界各國無法開發疫苗阻止疫情散播，現實上例如 SARS 和 MERS 都未有疫苗推出。武漢肺炎會否像這個模擬一樣帶來可怕的結局仍未可知，而政府的防疫決定，則是挽回人命傷亡的主要關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n有買趁早快啲買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0ed7cb9f638cdbf1e386b1860a5f73f58f6c1a","tid":1847864,"uid":339272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:26:45.000Z","msg":"買既唔係都驚失業咩"},{"pid":"ebf2fa4bc8909a39583d1357b237c814d7967312","tid":1847864,"uid":24697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d0ed7cb9f638cdbf1e386b1860a5f73f58f6c1a","tid":1847864,"uid":339272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:26:45.000Z","msg":"買既唔係都驚失業咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"有平盤先算"},{"pid":"9a958d862394df1c2ca23384b9268cc9c6bc4a6f","tid":1847864,"uid":157171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:17:25.000Z","msg":"15後去睇一睇，預8 折換樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0a37126936052afd5c8092854c327cf522c179","tid":1847864,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9d0ed7cb9f638cdbf1e386b1860a5f73f58f6c1a","tid":1847864,"uid":339272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:26:45.000Z","msg":"買既唔係都驚失業咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"連登仔一係full pay一係有父幹 邊會驚失業<br />\n況且住屋需求咁大 唔買又會驚遲啲井噴式上升"},{"pid":"f23d3aa9abac0c364e5619d8cc37802c69650879","tid":1847864,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:00:59.000Z","msg":"[狼人] 武漢肺炎大逃殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eY8gq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eY8gq.jpg&h=286709db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c05fe6e0f7e369ea2807e05c1c944481b664254","tid":1847864,"uid":2796